📸: @chestermarc

What an incredible honor it was to produce @americasyouthchoir for the Super Bowl LVII pre-game. 

@rneubs is the best. She brought @thebenbram @scotthoying and me onto this project to add some of our musical chops, and under her leadership, this piece turned out way better than I could’ve ever expected. 

Historically this piece has felt politicized, and this year, we chose to focus on the values that make this country amazing - diversity, ingenuity, and the hope for a better future. What better way to underscore these values — than with a beautiful and talented choir made up of American youths. 

On a personal note, and Ben so aptly pointed this out, it is very cool to see the surname Ahmed credited on such a patriotic American piece with so many eyes on it. In a country that has grappled with decades of Islamophobia, this feels like a small triumph to say the least. 

Please tune in and enjoy this piece 🙂

📸: @tory.stolper

EMMY-NOMINATED?! 😱
I am so delighted that our Super Bowl LVII piece, ’Ragged Old Flag’ has been nominated for an Emmy award! Working on this was a major highlight of my year so far, and seeing it positively affect so many people was a huge win. But now, to be nominated for such a prestigious award feels totally surreal!

We are nominated in two categories - one for camera work, and the other for our direct contributions in Music Direction!!!

Congratulations to our team @rneubs @thebenbram @scotthoying @americasyouthchoir @copilotcorp. 

So freaking cool.

Eid Mubarak from your fave Muslim aca-siblings!

EMMY AWARD WINNERS!

Truly humbled that we have WON the Emmy Award for Best Music Direction for the “Ragged Old Flag”, the piece we produced/arranged/music directed for Super Bowl LVII! 

I’m overcome with emotion and pride for the amazing team that made this happen - for your colleagues to be brilliant collaborators and also the best friends - i feel so incredibly lucky. 

I actually didn’t know what to expect yesterday; I always felt like the true victory was putting a diverse group of talented young people in front of millions of Americans - and it *is*. But now, to receive this award and to be recognized for our efforts, the hard work by the kids and parents, the crew, everyone - it feels really special. 

@rneubs, thank you for your leadership and vision and thoughtfulness. @thebenbram and @scotthoying, look at us go!! 🥲 

Since the hardware will take a sec to arrive, I took a page out of Scott’s book and give you my best photoshop skills! 😂
I promise this one’s not photoshopped #emmywinner
